<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>

<head>
    <title>Register – AI Stroke Rehab</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial;
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, #0f172a, #1e3a8a);
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }


        .card {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            width: 350px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            text-align: center;
        }

        h2 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #1e3a8a;
        }

        input,
        select {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 8px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        button {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            border: none;
            background: #1e3a8a;
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        button:hover {
            background: #2563eb;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #1e3a8a;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="card">
        <h2>Create Account</h2>

        <form method="POST" action="/register">

            ```
            <input name="name" placeholder="Full Name" required>

            <input name="email" type="email" placeholder="Email" required>

            <input name="password" type="password" placeholder="Password" required>

            <!-- Stroke specific data -->
            <select name="strokeType">
                <option>Ischemic Stroke</option>
                <option>Hemorrhagic Stroke</option>
                <option>Other</option>
            </select>

            <select name="affectedSide">
                <option>Left Side</option>
                <option>Right Side</option>
                <option>Both</option>
            </select>

            <button>Register</button>
            ```

        </form>

        <p>Already registered? <a href="/">Login</a></p>
    </div>

</body>

</html>